Package: pkgmkr
Title: Create an R Package with One Simple Function
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Shaurita D.", family = "Hutchins", email = "shaurita.d.hutchins@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7687-0059", copyright_holder = "Shaurita D. Hutchins"))
Description: Simplifies the process of creating R packages by providing a single,
    straightforward function that handles package initialization, Git integration,
    license selection, README generation, and pkgdown site setup. Package creation
    can also be configured using YAML or JSON configuration files.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://shauritahutchins.com/pkgmkr/, https://github.com/sdhutchins/pkgmkr
BugReports: https://github.com/sdhutchins/pkgmkr/issues
